{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There's a killer with a keen eye and a thirst for blood stalking this city, and a hard-boiled detective losing his sanity trying to catch him. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389570/extras/SK_Title.gif?t=1730737185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Sniper Killer, you take on the role of both Detective Comardy and the cryptic &quot;Sniper Killer&quot; as the story unravels after each victim has their brains splattered across the ground by a well placed shot. From the scummy streets of the city to the state carnival, no location is safe from the Sniper's watchful eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389570/extras/headshot_small.gif?t=1730737185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How does he choose his victims? Does he have a motive for these seemingly random acts of atrocities? Can the burnt-out detective solve this case before even more bodies start piling up? This retro horror thriller is enough to make any true-crime fans pick up their detective hats and start searching for clues. Can you solve the case in time? Or will your head be just another target for the Sniper Killer? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389570/extras/comardy_small.gif?t=1730737185\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Sniper Killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2389570/1c8e76b2749ef813d0c868f03f7e361e18a05c27.jpg"},{"name":"Headshot Hotshot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2389570/a99b11de27aa91a9706d3c0c94590fa6fb680aed.jpg"},{"name":"Super Sleuth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2389570/ff4